  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878580/extras/8538b7da950ce8aa67ab982a009dde5f.poster.avif?t=1739398630\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878580/extras/8538b7da950ce8aa67ab982a009dde5f.webm?t=1739398630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878580/extras/8538b7da950ce8aa67ab982a009dde5f.mp4?t=1739398630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore the dark hallways of underground parking and find a passage to the hidden obscure underworld. Find new weapons and use them to survive. Solve the mystery of this cursed place and the monsters that inhabit it. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878580/extras/91f74e1b70e9bafdc70c9781bbd1a4c2.avif?t=1739398630\" width=616 height=138 /></span><li>Every weapon has its dedicated use in a battle against the mutants, the undead, and the military;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878580/extras/4327c65f4bf4b1460567d00c9f792ed9.avif?t=1739398630\" width=616 height=138 /></span><br></li><li>Unique gameplay combines survival, ammo management, shoot’em’up, and racing;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878580/extras/8be294135af7ecc5fe1f60856336938f.avif?t=1739398630\" width=616 height=138 /></span><br></li><li>Inspired by Splatterpunk storytelling style;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878580/extras/81f675425f34ba65fc7a7da7a9d77798.avif?t=1739398630\" width=616 height=138 /></span><br></li><li>Levels filled with secrets and challenges.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878580/extras/8538b7da950ce8aa67ab982a009dde5f.poster.avif?t=1739398630\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878580/extras/8538b7da950ce8aa67ab982a009dde5f.webm?t=1739398630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878580/extras/8538b7da950ce8aa67ab982a009dde5f.mp4?t=1739398630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore the dark hallways of underground parking and find a passage to the hidden obscure underworld. Find new weapons and use them to survive. Solve the mystery of this cursed place and the monsters that inhabit it. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878580/extras/91f74e1b70e9bafdc70c9781bbd1a4c2.avif?t=1739398630\" width=616 height=138 /></span><li>Every weapon has its dedicated use in a battle against the mutants, the undead, and the military;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878580/extras/4327c65f4bf4b1460567d00c9f792ed9.avif?t=1739398630\" width=616 height=138 /></span><br></li><li>Unique gameplay combines survival, ammo management, shoot’em’up, and racing;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878580/extras/8be294135af7ecc5fe1f60856336938f.avif?t=1739398630\" width=616 height=138 /></span><br></li><li>Inspired by Splatterpunk storytelling style;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878580/extras/81f675425f34ba65fc7a7da7a9d77798.avif?t=1739398630\" width=616 height=138 /></span><br></li><li>Levels filled with secrets and challenges.</li></ul>",
